{"page":1,"prev_page_endpoint":null,"next_page_endpoint":null,"total_pages":1,"reasons":[{"created_at":"2013-11-07T15:48:42Z","content":"I have talked to the counties I have talked to the OPP for the last 15 years. I live 200 feet from the corner the last police officer I talked to just shrugged it off when I told him people are going to die at that corner and it will be your fault. You have a OPP officer sitting at the corner of Headline road and Mc Connel handing out tickets because people don't come to a full stop but won't sit at the corner of Headline and 138 and give out tickets to people who use the turn lanes as passing lanes.","like_count":2,"author_name":"James Rutley","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68346909"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T13:36:07Z","content":"I avoid the 138 at all costs when possible.  I've witnessed a fatal crash at this intersection (Headline Rd/138) and I still shudder when I think it could have been prevented.  Traffic lights may not prevent \"all\" crashes, but will help a great deal.  (I believe the whole 138 is a \"death road\") :(","like_count":2,"author_name":"Natalie Ladouceur","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68333981"},{"created_at":"2013-11-27T06:01:46Z","content":"I have had too many close calls with my children from people using the turning lanes as passing lanes. This is our route to the kids doctors and the hospital!!! As well my son was involved in a serious accident there this summer where there was a head on collision involving the car right in front of him. Luckily he was ok but our vehicle was written off (an expense we did not need) and last we heard the girl that caused the accident is still in hospital!!! Scariest day of my life as a mother!!!","like_count":1,"author_name":"Shana Croteau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71015150"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T20:22:44Z","content":"I cross this intersection every day and it's a great concern for my safety.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Dana Fry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24389964"},{"created_at":"2013-11-12T10:51:08Z","content":"There have been far too many accidents along the stretch of what is Highway 138 and it's time that the Ministry steps up and corrects the problem whether it be the installation of traffic lights at intersections and/or the eventuality of making the road 4 lanes.  How many more accidents need to happen at that particular intersection before something is done?","like_count":1,"author_name":"Debbie Burns","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68898730"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T18:18:38Z","content":"I have family in Cornwall and St. Andrews.  Many people drive over the speed limit on HWY 138.  A light should slow them down.  Also drivers looking to turn left from Headline onto the 138 have a difficult time due to the amount of traffic in both directions.  My last visit (august 2013) I was northbound on the 138 when a driver pulled out onto the 138 (turning left) and forced me to almost come to a stop on the highway or exchange paint.  The window of opportunity for him to cross the southbound lane was minimal due to spacing between cars.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Mark Telewiak","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68359980"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T01:11:01Z","content":"Safer roads means safer communities.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Chantal Lalonde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68382195"},{"created_at":"2013-11-12T02:28:37Z","content":"I will not use the road anymore, there are too many fatalities","like_count":1,"author_name":"Jo Ann Langstaff","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24386906"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T13:54:49Z","content":"Too many accidents on this road","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kyle Empringham","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68464754"},{"created_at":"2013-11-11T22:27:12Z","content":"Friends and family use this highway daily. I have lost co-workers . We need something done with this problem","like_count":1,"author_name":"Judy Black","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68849512"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T13:58:54Z","content":"Witnessed a near miss at this intersection just 3 days ago when a car speeding south was passing vehicles turning left into Headline Road East on the right using the Right Hand Turn lane. There was a car turning left/south from the east who had for some reason stopped three quarters into the turn and the lady slammed her brakes on, squealing just past my front end where I was on Headline West waiting at the stop sign. I have been advocating this traffic light for years as making lefts into Headline from either direction or trying to cross Hwy 138 is a bit like Russian Roulette specifically because of drivers passing on the right using the Right Hand Turn lanes there.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Christopher  Fry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/24317521"},{"created_at":"2013-11-28T14:46:46Z","content":"I'm a school bus driver and do go on Headline Rd. 4 times a day and I really don't feel it's a safe intersection at all.  Installing lights would solve a lot of problems and make it safer for all.  Drivers passing in a turning lane just so they don't need to stop even the police are doing it.  No wonder there's so many accidents.  Obey the law.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Julie Roy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71295674"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T02:43:57Z","content":"many accidents","like_count":1,"author_name":"diane mroz","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/25290161"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T14:26:19Z","content":"Very important","like_count":1,"author_name":"Alan Sabourin","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68339054"},{"created_at":"2013-12-02T01:50:54Z","content":"Because I live very near this intersection. If you are turning from headline east going South towards Cornwall there is a curve that blocks oncoming traffic. This wouldn't be a problem but some drivers are travelling at over 80km/hr making it difficult to judge how close they really are. Also, the turning lane on the west side of headline is often used as a passing lane making it difficult for traffic comimg from Cornwall & turning west on headline Rd.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Matthew McConnell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/71712205"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T20:55:19Z","content":"I moved on headline on Oct 25th 2013 and since I have been there I have already heard of 3 collisions on the corner of headline and 138 hwy. we haven't even been living there for 2 weeks. There are too many people passing on the right shoulder when the person in front of them is turning left. I almost got hit myself already. It hasn't even started snowing yet which worries me.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Valerie Howat","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68254804"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T00:48:20Z","content":"I am an RN and the injuries that are seen due to accidents on this road range from minor to DEVASTATING. I promise you the lives that will be saved are worth the money invested.","like_count":1,"author_name":"Kristen Renwick-Marshall","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68279089"},{"created_at":"2013-11-14T00:11:07Z","content":"Many people think you can pass to go around cars that are turning and cause accidents and near misses.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Karen Coleman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69059405"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T21:35:37Z","content":"It is very important to me and my wife.. we travel to Ottawa often to visit family and friends. we also travel with our son too.. so please let's prevent future accidents and deaths.. thank you..","like_count":0,"author_name":"Eric McLean","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68261576"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T20:07:48Z","content":"My family drives this hwy daily, the deadly crashes need to stop","like_count":0,"author_name":"Allison Main","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70901405"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T00:28:27Z","content":"My friends grandchildren has to use this intersection","like_count":0,"author_name":"Louise Suggars","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70802529"},{"created_at":"2013-11-11T00:37:52Z","content":"to make people slow down and make this corner safer for everyone","like_count":0,"author_name":"Randy Shaver","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68739627"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T11:26:28Z","content":"It is something that must be done to help prevent so many accidents at this intersection.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melissa St.Louis","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68320368"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T07:58:55Z","content":"I drive through there six days a week and seen to many close calls.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Barry Bilmer","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68426488"},{"created_at":"2013-11-12T12:01:55Z","content":"I travel this road every week with my son. it is EXTREMELY dangerous. There needs to be lights put up.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Natalie Cooke","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68903653"},{"created_at":"2013-09-08T23:30:37Z","content":"I pass this intersection every day, the way the traffic has increased makes it a real safety concern.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Cindy Rowe","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/61829162"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T02:40:30Z","content":"It's so appalling the millions in tax money this government wasted and with no accountability yet to save a human life from tragedy a petition has to be circulated for action. The lights on this corner should have been a no brainer long ago.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Tommy Sauve","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70823507"},{"created_at":"2013-11-25T17:30:18Z","content":"Safety reasons","like_count":0,"author_name":"Heather Myers","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70752918"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T23:20:32Z","content":"because people are getting hurt and or dying PUT A LIGHT UP BECAUSE IF THAT IS ONE OF MY FAMILY MEMBERS THAT GET HURT OR DIE BECAUSE OF NO TRAFFIC 