y Lalonde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68319727"},{"created_at":"2013-11-11T14:15:30Z","content":"I work in Cornwall and drive by that intersection everyday, and it is dangerous!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debbie Froats","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68795428"},{"created_at":"2014-01-10T14:24:39Z","content":"Many scares driving north and south.  Drivers using exit lanes as passing lane. Very scary when a car suddenly shows up passing a stopped vehicle and a car shows up passing in your lane.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ray Alguire","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/75738473"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T15:59:17Z","content":"I lived on County Road 44 (Headline Rd E) for over 20 years of my life, my parents still do, and I have always found that corner to be a danger zone. The number of people who run the stop sign to beat the south and north bound traffic is unbelievable! Not to mention the many local walkers/joggers/bikers who cross from one side of Headline  to the other in order to get to the bike path. It took how many years (and how many unfortunate and preventable deaths) for the light to go up on the corner of McConnell and South Branch - too many people I knew were victims of accidents there and I would really hate for something more to happen at the corner of Headline and 138 in order to see a light go up! I understand that by having a light put up will not eliminate ALL accidents, but it will at least help the flow of traffic and drivers to maintain their speed and be more alert.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Amanda Rudy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/63025526"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T21:00:06Z","content":"I travel this road everyday.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Elise Caron","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68255539"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T20:25:57Z","content":"I Drove this road almost weekly with my kids for hockey games and it is very dangerous","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lynn Tourangeau","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68249864"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T14:35:35Z","content":"I've seen on average 2-3 serious accidents a year at this corner. Many people who attempt to go around a vehicle that is waiting to turn east or west, have near misses because they do not want to slow down. There should be at least a turning lane to go east or west. Proper painted turning lane lines so people who don't know how to drive, don't place lives at risk. The road needs to be widened to allow for turning lanes, in all directions and traffic lights will take away most if the risks taken to simply get on or off this 138 hwy. This is a very dangerous intersection!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Pete Bray","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68340080"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T04:02:05Z","content":"I don't travel this Hwy, but I am sickened by the amount of accidents here! If traffic lights help, by all means, put them up!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Patti Adams","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70830892"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T15:40:31Z","content":"This is my home town and near my family's house, it is a very dangerous intersection to get out onto the 138 from Headline Road.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Erin Fry","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68346210"},{"created_at":"2013-11-11T14:40:39Z","content":"my mother travels this road and i have been to many accidents there","like_count":0,"author_name":"Sandy Roy","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68797620"},{"created_at":"2013-11-23T01:25:24Z","content":"To many accidents!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Michelle cardinal","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70486899"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T21:45:48Z","content":"I'm from Cornwall originally and still go there about 3 or 4 times a month. It's a stretch of road we now avoid simply because it's so incredibly dangerous. Not just the intersection in question but rather the entire road with people being impatient and whatnot. Just a terrible road to beg