 Ce Longchamps","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/69995344"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T00:32:49Z","content":"We need the traffic lights here.  There is a school near by and this is an accident waiting to happen.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Brenda  Coleman","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/21738083"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T01:52:37Z","content":"So less people die.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Jason McNamara","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70815910"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T01:16:24Z","content":"I also avoid 138 any time possible. Have had 2 family members involved in separate fatal crashes on this highway-including my cousin who died on the scene. Both crashes were head-on with the other vehicle crossing onto oncoming traffic. ","like_count":0,"author_name":"carole laferriere","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/41458357"},{"created_at":"2013-11-11T21:09:38Z","content":"I'm not sure this photograph on this page is actually at the intersection.  Mis-representation?  Anyway, I do agree that's a bad spot.  Perhaps a center turn lane would stop people from going around in the shoulder.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Marc Houde","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68840045"},{"created_at":"2013-11-23T09:35:45Z","content":"I travel Hwy 138 daily.  Very seldom do you see a Police cruiser.  People are treating the 138 as they do the 401.  Normal driving people are not safe on the 138.  More stop lights and more police presence would make speeding motorists, slow down!  The yellow caution light at Bonville does NO good either, when turning on Myer's Road, motorists are trying to pass you.  People don't slow down when you are turning, it is a scary road to be on.  MORE LIGHTS PLEASE, ALL ALONG THE HIGHWAY.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Debbie Killoran","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70507504"},{"created_at":"2013-11-22T18:12:59Z","content":"To many deaths on this road over stupidity","like_count":0,"author_name":"Lila Aubin","author_url":"