eding and heading your way with no way to back up with other vehicles behind you, is scary. Also with the additional of traffic light we also need more opp surveying the area for speeders.","like_count":0,"author_name":"Shelley Leroux","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68293538"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T07:06:38Z","content":"BECAUSE OF OUR SAFETY AND OTHERS ON THE ROAD. WHEN YOU HAVE SMALL CHILDREN YOU WORRY ABOUT EVERYTHING AND THIS ROAD DOES WORRY ME","like_count":0,"author_name":"Ashley Manwell","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68420553"},{"created_at":"2013-11-07T14:36:12Z","content":"My brother was killed on this road at the age of 7 given the fast trafic.  The problem has lasted too long.  Don't you think","like_count":0,"author_name":"Melanie Perrault","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68340148"},{"created_at":"2013-11-25T14:39:05Z","content":"For safety of everyone !","like_count":0,"author_name":"Maryse Gagnon Ruest","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70733592"},{"created_at":"2013-11-06T20:29:45Z","content":"How great would it be to prevent tragedy!!","like_count":0,"author_name":"Kristy Cartwright","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/68254305"},{"created_at":"2013-11-26T12:13:40Z","content":"It is a dangerous intersection and with all the fast drivers, texting drivers, the roads are getting more dangerous. Need to save lifes","like_count":0,"author_name":"Helen McKenzie","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/52919709"},{"created_at":"2013-11-27T05:12:31Z","content":"This is important to me because my friends and family cross that intersection every day.  I also agree that the use of the turning lane as a passing lane is an accident waiting to happen. The traffic is heavy and it is difficult to get a clear path to cross the intersection. Why is this important to you? (Optional)","like_count":0,"author_name":"stephane godard","author_url":"http://api.change.org/u/70998853"},{"created_at":"2013-11-08T12:47:14Z","content":"safety","like_co